item.description:
Sat 4/24 "Club Bohemia" downstairs $8

8:30 Get there at least 30 minutes ahead to get to grab a few small round tables up front at this club. It will be standing room only by 8:45PM

9:00 CELLO CHIX You are going to be blown away by the big sound of Jimmy Hendrix' "Purple Haze" on cello!!! I have seen them before and can't wait to see again.

10:00 ESTHEMA Do you crave world fusion jazz the way I do? Acoustic balkin, middle eastern, latin fused into one jazz sound is nothing like you have ever heard before. Tanya, Deepa and I have seen them twice before

11:00 The Ground Up

12:00 Dirty Water Brass Band
